						<p>Below the above inscription.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Ānanda.</hi></p>						

						<p>States that, under the orders of Nummatānu Sāhēbu Nārāyana-Reddi dug out a canal near Chāgallu and assigned <hi rend="italic">daśavandha</hi> land for its upkeep.</p>						

